'''老虎部隊'''（Qawat Al-Nimr，{{lang-ar|قوات النمر}}）為{{tsl|en|Syrian Arab Army|敘利亞陸軍}}轄下的的[[特種部隊|特種部隊]]，主要負責政府軍在[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]的攻勢。雖然老虎部隊的作戰成果相當傑出，但由於人數限制，無法同時進行多項攻勢<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/exclusive-tiger-forces-to-redeploy-to-northern-hama/|title=Exclusive: Tiger Forces to Redeploy to Northern Hama|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2015-11-10|accessdate=2016-02-12|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216013613/http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/exclusive-tiger-forces-to-redeploy-to-northern-hama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然在正式編制裏被稱爲師，但根據對部隊人數的估計，老虎部隊的實際規模較爲接近營<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://southfront.org/syrian-armys-tiger-forces-history-and-capabilities/|title=Syrian Army's Tiger Forces: History And Capabilities|date=2017-02-14|accessdate=2018-02-12|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171120020914/https://southfront.org/syrian-armys-tiger-forces-history-and-capabilities/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
2013年秋天，[[蘇赫爾·哈桑|蘇赫爾·哈桑]]上校在[[拉塔基亞省|拉塔基亞省]]和[[哈馬省|哈馬省]]的軍事行動取得成功後，被[[叙利亚武装力量|叙利亚武装力量]]中央指派組建及訓練一支以進攻為主要任務的特種部隊。海珊上校挑選了一些士兵並逐漸演變為老虎部隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/colonel-suheil-al-hassan-tiger-forces/|title=Who is Colonel Suheil al-Hassan of the Tiger Forces?|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2015-02-26|accessdate=2016-02-12|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612190401/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/colonel-suheil-al-hassan-tiger-forces/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年12月25日，海珊在前一年拒絕了[[准將|-{准}-將]]軍銜後，被擢升為[[少将|少将]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-commander-promoted-to-major-general/|title=Prominent Tiger Forces Commander Promoted to Major General|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2015-12-15|accessdate=2016-06-05|archive-date=2018-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717055009/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-commander-promoted-to-major-general/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海珊在[[阿勒頗攻勢_(2016年6月－9月)|2016年的阿勒頗攻勢]]扮演了重要的角色，曾截斷連接當時被反對派占領的[[阿勒颇|阿勒頗]]的主要補給綫。

在[[俄羅斯在敘利亞內戰的軍事介入|俄羅斯軍事介入敘利亞]]後，老虎部隊獲得了一些陸戰裝備，包括[[AK-74突击步枪|AK-74M]]和1P87準直式瞄準鏡<ref name=":0" />。此部隊為敘利亞陸軍中少數首先部署[[T-90主戰坦克|T-90主戰坦克]]的部隊之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-mobilize-t-90-tanks-upcoming-aleppo-offensive/|title=Tiger Forces mobilize T-90 tanks for upcoming Aleppo offensive|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2016-05-28|accessdate=2016-06-07|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630023613/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-mobilize-t-90-tanks-upcoming-aleppo-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/convoy-of-russian-t-90-tanks-arrive-in-southern-aleppo/|title=Convoy of Russian T-90 tanks arrive in southern Aleppo|author=Leith Fadel|work=Al-Masdar News|date=2016-01-23|accessdate=2016-06-08|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630090036/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/convoy-of-russian-t-90-tanks-arrive-in-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其餘部隊為第四裝甲師和沙漠之鷹旅<ref name=":1" />。

老虎部隊最爲著名和有效的戰術是從多個方向探測敵軍，找出弱點並派出大量機械部隊從該處突破敵軍防綫<ref name=":0" />。

